---
title: Chicken & Spinach Salad with Cheesy Roasted Zucchini and Tomatoes
description: You won’t have to convince anyone to finish their veggies tonight. These cheesy roasted vegetables will convert even the pickiest of eaters. Coated with a layer of parmesan, mozzarella, and panko, you’ll be fighting over the last bite!
